For the second time, major Peter Mugure failed to take plea at the Nyeri high court after he was arraigned on today. Mugure was arraigned on December 6th before high court Jairus Ngaa who ordered for a psychiatric test to be conducted. Mugure is the prime suspect in the murder of his wife joyce syombua and their two children.his co?accused Collins Pamba is also in custody at Kerugoya GK prison and he is scheduled to take plea on Thursday this week